OL,3,CMPs call on government to extend paid
OL,4,Cbereavement leave to cover miscarriages
OL,6,FWomen and their partners should be
OL,7,Fentitled to paid bereavement leave if
OL,8,Fthey experience a miscarriage, MPs
OL,9,Fhave recommended.
OL,11,FThe Women and Equalities Committee say
OL,12,Fthe current sick leave provision is an
OL,13,F"inappropriate and inadequate form of
OL,14,Femployer support" for couples after a
OL,15,Fmiscarriage.
