OL,3,CMPs call on government to extend paid
OL,4,Cbereavement leave to cover miscarriages
OL,6,FEmployees are currently eligible for
OL,7,Fstatutory parental bereavement leave
OL,8,Fand pay if there's a stillbirth after
OL,9,F24 weeks of pregnancy, but there is no
OL,10,Fspecific leave for a pre-24 week loss
OL,11,Fin the form of miscarriage.
OL,13,FThe committee said the two-week leave
OL,14,Fperiod should be also made available
OL,15,Fto those bereaved as a result of pre-
OL,16,F24 week pregnancy loss.
