OL,3,CMPs call on government to extend paid
OL,4,Cbereavement leave to cover miscarriages
OL,6,FThe committee said an estimated more
OL,7,Fthan one in five pregnancies end
OL,8,Fbefore 24 weeks, with between 10% and
OL,9,F20% of pregnancies ending in the first
OL,10,F12 weeks, known as early miscarriage.
OL,12,FMinister Darren Jones signaled the
OL,13,Fcommittee's recommendation is
OL,14,Fsomething government could enact when
OL,15,Fasked about it on Wednesday.
OL,17,F"The Deputy Prime Minister will be
OL,18,Flooking at the campaign in detail, of
OL,19,Fcourse it feels right we should
OL,20,Fsupport people in those
OL,21,Fcircumstances", he told ITV News.
