OL,3,CMPs call on government to extend paid
OL,4,Cbereavement leave to cover miscarriages
OL,6,FWhile MPs acknowledged that a "growing
OL,7,Fnumber of employers have specific
OL,8,Fpregnancy loss leave and pay
OL,9,Fpolicies", such as NHS Trusts and the
OL,10,FCo-op, they said there remain "very
OL,11,Fsubstantial gaps in provision".
OL,13,FThey welcomed recent progress
OL,14,Finvolving the introduction of baby
OL,15,Floss certificates but said this "does
OL,16,Fnot go far enough and it should be
OL,17,Fbacked up by statutory support".
