OL,3,CMPs call on government to extend paid
OL,4,Cbereavement leave to cover miscarriages
OL,6,FThe committee said: "There is no
OL,7,Fstatutory acknowledgement of the grief
OL,8,Fmany women and their partners will
OL,9,Ffeel after a pre-24-week pregnancy
OL,10,Floss and the effects this may have on
OL,11,Ftheir working lives."
OL,13,FThe committee heard that sick pay is
OL,14,Ftoo little for many women and their
OL,15,Fpartners to be able to afford to take
OL,16,Fthe time off they need, while it also
OL,17,Fdoes not offer the confidentiality
OL,18,Fmany women want, with employees often
OL,19,Frequired to report the reason for
OL,20,Ftheir absence directly to their line
OL,21,Fmanager.
