OL,6,FCommittee chairwoman Sarah Owen has
OL,7,Fpreviously spoken of her own loss,
OL,8,Fsaying she was "not prepared for the
OL,9,Fgrief of miscarrying".
OL,11,FThe committee said it intends to put
OL,12,Fforward amendments to the Employment
OL,13,FRights Bill.
