OL,3,CMPs call on government to extend paid
OL,4,Cbereavement leave to cover miscarriages
OL,6,FIt said: "They seek to extend the same
OL,7,Fentitlements to statutory parental
OL,8,Fbereavement leave and pay as are
OL,9,Fcurrently available to parents
OL,10,Fbereaved by the loss of children and
OL,11,Fstillbirths to employees who
OL,12,Fexperience pre-24-week pregnancy
OL,13,Flosses.
OL,15,F"This would include those who
OL,16,Fexperience miscarriage, ectopic
OL,17,Fpregnancy, molar pregnancy, in vitro
OL,18,Ffertilisation embryo transfer loss,
OL,19,Fand terminations for medical reasons."
